The paper presents a method for freeway merge based on multipolicy decision making coupled with a reinforcement learning technique called passive actor-critic (pAC). This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The method is applied to a real-world scenario involving traffic, which suggests that the paper may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. Additionally, the paper may involve computer vision techniques for processing traffic data, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) category.
